Note that the lower bound 'shelly >= 1.9' is needed because of major
breakage.

Suite test-bugs: also remove generated *.hi files, for multi-GHC environments

Old GHCs (e.g. 8.0) crash when there is already a `.hi` file generated
by a newer GHC.
Fix whitespace violations and remove -fwarn-tabs (included in -Wall)

Remove obsolete PATH manipulation in testsuite

Program c2hs is now on the PATH by virtue of `build-tools: c2hs` in
the `.cabal` file.
Disable broken part of testcase #102
Enable -Wcompat for GHC >= 8

Use ghc-paths to determine path of ghc executable

This enables working in multi-GHC environments.  In particular,
```
    cabal test -w <ghc>
```
will use `<ghc>` as "ghc" also in the testsuite.
Since shelly-1.9, Shelly.FilePath is just Prelude.FilePath
Fix whitespace violations and remove -fwarn-tabs (included in -Wall)
Allow shelly-1.10; Haskell CI for GHC 7.10 - 9.2
